      <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Accessibility statement</h1>

      <p>This accessibility statement applies to content published on the prison-visits.service.justice.gov.uk domain.</p>

      <p>This website is run by HM Prison and Probation Service (HMPPS). We want as many people as possible to be able to use this website.</p>

      <p>It is currently in a pilot stage and has not been fully tested for accessibility. An accessibility audit is planned for summer 2024.</p>
      
      <p>We will make improvements to accessibility as we find issues.</p>
      
      <p>
        <a href="https://mcmw.abilitynet.org.uk/" target="_blank">AbilityNet</a>
        has advice on making your device easier to use if you have a disability.
      </p>

